 table, it is a multifunctional modular furniture\n\" class=\"wp-image-36477\" title=\"Modular dining table that transforms into a pool table, it is a multifunctional modular furniture\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/30125827\/modular-dining-table-transforms-into-pool-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/30125827\/modular-dining-table-transforms-into-pool-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/30125827\/modular-dining-table-transforms-into-pool-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/30125827\/modular-dining-table-transforms-into-pool-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>&nbsp;Enjoy gaming weekends in the comfort of your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, whether you are a loner, party animal or family person, the various types of modular furniture mentioned in this blog will help you turn your home into a fun weekend paradise. And if you want to know which type of home interior design will match this modular furniture, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">book a free consultation<\/a> with us today. Our designers will help you with personalised home interior designs that suit your budget and lifestyle.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=